			"editorData": {
				"HowToTrigger": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "- Load up GustavDev/SCL_Main_A\r\n- Use ReCon command \"oe MemLib_AllJars\" to get all the brain jars and teleport to the Brain Reading Device.\r\n- In front of you will be a severed head and a receptacle to its left. Insert the appropriate brain jar into the receptacle by interacting with it - the jar is called \"Dark Mind\".\r\n- After inserting the jar, it will appear on top of the receptacle and you can talk to the severed head for the dialogue to start.\r\n- This jar is one of the two jars that can be found in the tutorial level (Nautiloid)."
				},
